content.description:
This is another ridiculous eliminate. Start on the jug just above waist level on the right side of the south roof. Throw far left to an six-inch-long finger-pad edge on the left side of the lip of the roof. Match on it. Throw straight up past the seam (

Tommy's Way

) to the next edge. This one has a bit of a lip, so watch out for flappers. Now pull the feet over the roof, and top it out.
